<H3>* THE BUSINESS CLIMATE IN GUINEA *</H3>
<UL>
<A HREF = "#1"><A HREF = "#1"><LI>GUINEA - HIGHLIGHTS, 18-MONTH & FIVE-YEAR FORECASTS,&nbsp;RISK FACTORS, POLITICAL, ECONOMIC, AND SOCIAL DATA</A>&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp<NOBR>(1497 words)</NOBR></LI>
